<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>文档规范 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/</link><description>文档规范 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>技术写作</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E4%B8%8E%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%86%99%E4%BD%9C/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E4%B8%8E%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%86%99%E4%BD%9C/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="技术写作">技术写作</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：技术写作的核心目标是降低知识传递成本，通过结构化表达让不同背景的读者快速理解复杂概念，好文档的标准是&quot;只看标题和代码就能懂&quot;。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="技术文档通过分层信息结构和可视化手段让受众按需获取所需深度">技术文档通过分层信息结构和可视化手段，让受众按需获取所需深度</h2>
<h3 id="文档分层阅读设计">文档分层阅读设计</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">第一层（30秒）：标题 + 核心结论 → 了解是什么
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">第二层（3分钟）：小标题 + 表格/列表 → 了解关键点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">第三层（15分钟）：代码示例 + 详细说明 → 了解怎么做
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">第四层（按需）：参考链接 + 扩展阅读 → 深入了解原理</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="技术文档结构模板">技术文档结构模板</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-markdown">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gh"># 标题（结论性陈述）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">&gt; </span><span class="ge">核心结论：1-3句话概括全文要点
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">---
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">## 一、上层概括（以上统下）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">### 子标题1
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">-</span> 要点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">-</span> 要点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">### 子标题2
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">-</span> 要点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">-</span> 要点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">## 二、常见问题与误区
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">### 问题1：...
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">**根因**：...
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gs">**解决**</span>：...
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">## 三、参考
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- [<span class="nt">相关文档</span>](<span class="na">./link.md</span>)</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="表达技巧">表达技巧</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>技巧</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>示例</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>结论先行</td>
          <td>先说结果，再说过程</td>
          <td>&ldquo;连接池不足导致超时，解决方案是…&rdquo;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>数据说话</td>
          <td>用数字代替&quot;很多&quot;&ldquo;很快&rdquo;</td>
          <td>&ldquo;QPS从1000提升到5000&rdquo;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>对比呈现</td>
          <td>好坏对照</td>
          <td>❌错误写法 / ✅正确写法</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>代码说话</td>
          <td>用示例代替长描述</td>
          <td>直接给出配置代码</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>图表辅助</td>
          <td>一图胜千言</td>
          <td>架构图、流程图、时序图</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
